subject: Swimming
Sexual Harassment
Suits and Litigation
lead_paragraph: A 21-year-old former competitive swimmer from Kansas accused her swim club coach of sexual misconduct and claimed USA Swimming and her swim club were negligent in protecting her and others from him.
